    "It also displayed commendable performance on challenging targets that featured a sparse number of acceptable models.",
    "Furthermore, ComplexQA is capable of delivering a detailed assessment of each interface residue, offering a level of precision that is invaluable in the field of protein complex structure analysis.",
    "(https://huggingface.co/nferruz/ProtGPT2), a cutting-edge autoregressive transformer model grounded in language-based principles, has been engineered to de novo construct protein structures with high throughput efficiency (Ferruz et al., 2022).",
